  <data name="Label3.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>5/7/2026:
Windows v1.6.1
Launcher:
- Changed Challenge List Redirect Link

In Game:
- Added custom patches to Geode Mod "Simple Patch Loader"

19/4/2026:
2.1 GDPS v1.6: Pointercrate Update
- The Demon List has entered Version 2, with a whole new interface
  and account system, similar to Pointercrate! Thanks to kacygd 
  for the source code and making this happen!
- Fixed version number in launcher
- Replaced Twitter icon with GDPSHub icon
- Along with the new gradient background is now available on Android!

25/3/2026:
Windows v1.5.5
- Changed Gradient Background
- Readded Mega Hack Recolor (lets you color the mod menu to
  your likings)
- Added Input Lag Fix
- Added Music Offset Minute Support (lets you set the offset
  using minutes &lt;mm:ss&gt;)

16/3/2026:
Windows v1.5.4.3 (Hotfix)
- Updated the FAQ page in the launcher
- a little bit more splash text
STILL NOT A LAUNCHER RECODE BTW

1/2/2026:
Windows v1.5.4.2 (Hotfix)
- Change GDPS Directory from "C:\Program Files (x86)\2.1 GDPS"
  to "C:\Users\AppData\Roaming\2.1 GDPS”
- Even more splash text :3

17/1/2026:
Windows v1.5.4.1 (Hotfix)
- fix issues when modifying gdps program files folder

14th December 2025:
Windows 1.5.4 (Jolly Edition) Released!
Lets feel a little bit jolly today

Launcher:
- Added "Start GDPS on Launch"
  (Incompatible with Geode unfortunately)

In-Game:
- Changed Menu Music to
  "Guardian Tales OST: Lobby - Christmas, Day" (the ost is so cool)
- Readded FPS Bypass with a little twist!!

7th December 2025:
Hotfix 1.5.3.1 Released!
- Removed ConcurrentHTTP as it causes problems on other mods

2nd December 2025:
Windows 1.5.3 Released!
Launcher:
- Added Github button
- Updated the FAQ page

In-Game:
- Added ConcurrentHTTP (Allows for download multiple things at once)
- Added AutoPause (Automatically pause when losing focus or resizing)
- Added BetterSave (AutomaticallyBacks up your data whenever the
  game closes)
- Added Playtest Fix (Fixes the issue where toggling preview mode
  while playtesting in BetterEdit would break levels)

11th November 2025:
Windows 1.5.2.2 Released!
Added "Auto Check for Updates"
Added an option to close the launcher after launch

20th October 2025:
Windows 1.5.2 Released!
Geode Support!
We now have Geode compatibility for 2.1 GDPS!
Thanks to DimisAIO!

21st September 2025:
Windows v1.5.1 Released!
Launcher:
- Renamed "What's New?" Button to "Settings" Button
- Changelogs, FAQ and Credits are now moved to "Settings" window
- Added Discord RPC to the launcher
- Removed the ability to minimize the settings windows
- Added the ability to switch between Demon List and Challenge List

In Game:
- Added Demons in Garage (allows you to view your demon count
  in the icon kit)
- Added Startpos Fix (fixes the lag when playing with startpos or
  practice mode)
- Added Effect Lines Fix (fixes the effect lines not showing sometimes)

5th September 2025:
Windows v1.5 Released!
A new launcher for 2.1 GDPS was made for more simple and easier
experience!

24th August 2025:
GDPSFH is now back! You can now replay 2.1 GDPS.

22nd August 2025:
GDPSFH is down due to drive failure. Server will be up in 2-3 days.

1st August 2025:
Windows Update v1.4.41

- Switched from ProxyDLLLoader (adaf-dll loader) to QuickLDR
by HJFod for more stability
- Removed InputLagFix
- Added Alt Tab Fix 
(Fixes the Bug with Volume Control Mod where if you alt tab and 
then open GD back up, it'll still think you're holding alt)

5th June 2025:
Windows Update v1.4.4

- Removed AutoPause as well as some mods that might have cause
  crashes
- Added Timestamp Fix and Sum Attempts Mod
- Reverted the Song Search Mod Replacement change

31st May 2025:
Classic Map Pack Released!

30th May 2025:
New Quests are added! Good Luck!

Windows v1.4.3

- Removed FPS Bypass mod as it causes alot of crashes
- Removed level name when playtesting a level in discord rpc

