  <data name="Label4.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>How do I register?
- You can register through the dashboard or inside the GDPS.

My account is disabled? What do i do?
- In the login page, click the "Activate Acc" button. If that doesnt
  work, activate your account in the dashboard.

Where are the GDPS files located?
- They are located in AppData\Roaming\2.1 GDPS

How do I install mods?
- (QuickLDR) Put the mods inside the quickldr folder, copy the entire
  name of the file, go to settings.txt and paste the file in.
  (MH Extensions/GDMegaOverlay) Just drag in the mod into their
  own mod loader folder.

How do I install Mega Hack?
- Install the v7 installer, then select "2.1 GDPS.exe" in the directory
  chooser.

Can I hack?
- 1 answer, no.
  You can view the following allowed hacks and mods in our discord
  server.

I dont have Mega Hack. Is there any other mod menu for free?
- Yes. Personally, I use GDMO because its the closest to free Mega
  Hack, but you can choose what mod menu you want. (Ex: GDHM)

Can i use GDPS Switcher for this?
- This is a 2.1 GDPS brother, so no.

Theres other problems while playing this GDPS. Are there any fix?
- There are more FAQ and fixes in our discord server.

</value>
